Package: OAtools
Title: Analysis of OpenArray qPCR Data
Version: 0.99.0
Description: Provides an automated pipeline to analyze gene expression 
    experiments on the OpenArray real-time PCR platform. OAtools fits
    logistic regressions to fluorescence curves to distinguish between 
    real amplification and false positives. OAtools supports data import, 
    analysis, and visualization through plots and a dynamic .html report.
